{"tid":1493675,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"保護九龍公園","createTime":"2019-08-21T10:25:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T13:32:13.000Z","uid":283061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0736afa7d481f5ca24178bfe8c49fc269df2e62c","tid":1493675,"uid":283061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T10:25:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K3Ss1H9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK3Ss1H9.jpg&h=b5504564&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nmola mola! 九龍公園300棵樹就嚟無喇😭<br />\n睇埋個地下空間嘅設計，根本就無助增加𣈱達性，建設更多零售更可能增加人流，令尖沙咀一帶變得更擠逼。<br />\n　<br />\n今日係公眾諮詢最後一日，請直接撰寫簡單的意見書表明反對，並電郵至：<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">info_urbanunderground@aecom.com</span></span>或者喺觀鳥會簽署<a href=\"https://protectkowloonpark.weebly.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fprotectkowloonpark.weebly.com%2F&d=0fhT0ZiErqSmjIt08Df9on0iZiuoirEQNng52NyFBY4%3D&h=1f812064\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://protectkowloonpark.weebly.com/</a><br />\n　<br />\n雖然諮詢網頁內有問卷讓公眾發表意見，不過填之前要留意‼️勿誤墮陷阱‼️<br />\n　<br />\n由於問卷設計基本上以贊成開鑿地下空間為前設，因此大家填寫時要小心，不要填寫擬建用途及施工計劃，否則可能被引用為支持開設地下空間。同埋唔好懶啊！一定要喺其他意見中寫上「反對開設地下空間」！<br />\n<br />\n‼️陷阱問卷在此‼️<a href=\"https://www.urbanunderground.gov.hk/public_engagement2.php#opinion\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.urbanunderground.gov.hk%2Fpublic_engagement2.php%23opinion&d=0fhT0ZiErqSmjIt08Df9on0iZiuoirEQNng52NyFBY4%3D&h=a52f37c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.urbanunderground.gov.hk/public_engagement2.php#opinion</a><br />\n　<br />\n#守護九龍公園 #反對開鑿地下空間<br />\n---------------------------<br />\n【環保觸覺就「九龍公園開設地下空間」意見書】<br />\n．<br />\n環保觸覺認為九龍公園的完整性及綠化功能相當重要，因此反對政府提議於九龍公園開設地下空間，原因如下：<br />\n．<br />\n(一)  工程嚴重傷害樹木<br />\n開設地下空間難免會傷害樹木根部及泥土層，而多個明挖回填的開展位置都是樹木林立，該批樹木很大機會因工程而被移除或移植。<br />\n．<br />\n(二)  無需增加暢達性<br />\n政府指地下空間可使尖沙咀周邊更四通八達，但現時九龍公園已有多條行人道及出入口，十分便捷，因此根本無需利用地下空間以增加暢達性。<br />\n．<br />\n(三)  地下空間並無作用<br />\n政府文件指地下空間可作文娛康樂，並有少量零售。可是，尖沙咀已有很多零售樓面，而九龍公園本身已提供一個上佳的消閒地方給市民。政府此舉似是為增設地下空間而增設地下空間，並沒有具環保、公義及有利市民的目的。<br />\n．<br />\n(四)  改善人流弄巧反拙<br />\n我們認為增加地下空間，只會增加人流。政府若想改善人車爭路，最佳方法是減少大陸自由行，例如近月旅客數字減少，尖沙咀及海傍一帶，亦變得較適合遊人參觀及休息。<br />\n．<br />\n(五)  工程只會徒添爭議<br />\n在九龍公園開設地下空間所費不菲，但又作用有限，更傷害環境，實屬重蹈過往政府濫建大白象的軌跡，恐怕會使民怨升温，徒添社會爭議。<br />\n．<br />\n誠希政府撤回項目，不應破壞環境，也不應製造不必要的爭議。"},{"pid":"6a85f1919f24b514588964badae169602cee7844","tid":1493675,"uid":58868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T10:26:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6e130ba5b084cfb6ddc329316ef347a17eae81df","tid":1493675,"uid":283061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T10:26:31.000Z","msg":"自推十次"},{"pid":"8d70fd51fc318160a01c565354698bcce4439a04","tid":1493675,"uid":283061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T10:26:47.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"c3a34d82938307964c36849d9378fa70576d37b2","tid":1493675,"uid":283061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T10:27:01.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"f7c2959e390e2b2d4ea0d988c66cf6a96e17fe41","tid":1493675,"uid":283061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T10:27:15.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"f6094c96a64a935875316f8169716bbef0db22d3","tid":1493675,"uid":283061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T10:27:26.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"7d7ba8d091803341faf1aa6f89ebf825738e832b","tid":1493675,"uid":283061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T10:27:38.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"ec11a59ba3ded48f502a05a7875f20973f301aff","tid":1493675,"uid":283061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T10:27:50.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"11da31aaedb6d0b1cb335a61ebc3ed98967d6e3f","tid":1493675,"uid":283061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T10:28:00.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"d1c13e00637df3c061669535d0c327c0d4d71cd3","tid":1493675,"uid":283061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T10:28:10.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"d49c9fc8103ab0e337adf85b13d094642ffa0c55","tid":1493675,"uid":283061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T10:28:20.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"54051928a1619d42cb42a862c02cd91e76045578","tid":1493675,"uid":283061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T10:28:33.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"9119e2629a641a62bd631f960b58de4288f18f85","tid":1493675,"uid":167619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T10:30:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HAcHQEm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHAcHQEm.jpg&h=fd3f4d37&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1882c80d2b075a33e6a7e58191166078e9b79f2c","tid":1493675,"uid":283061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T10:36:20.000Z","msg":"雖然我唔係保育L,但希望可以守護嗰300棵樹,今日係最後一日提交意見,希望大家一人一Email 反對300棵樹被移除"},{"pid":"f3bf7da7b1311f7ec2d7cda802ccd144a0e8c65b","tid":1493675,"uid":118922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1882c80d2b075a33e6a7e58191166078e9b79f2c","tid":1493675,"uid":283061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T10:36:20.000Z","msg":"雖然我唔係保育L,但希望可以守護嗰300棵樹,今日係最後一日提交意見,希望大家一人一Email 反對300棵樹被移除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T13:32:13.000Z","msg":"我唔制，唔想香港起呢啲， 個公園有好多動物住嫁"}]}